Subject: Re: Breech Baby Info Needed
Message-ID: <1993Apr5.184453.8394@cs.rochester.edu>
Date: 5 Apr 93 18:44:53 GMT
References: <TIGGER.93Apr2110251@satyr.Sylvan.COM> <1993Apr3.161757.19612@cs.rochester.edu> <1993Apr5.151818.27409@trentu.ca>
