Subject: Re: Striato Nigral Degeneration
Message-ID: <19390@pitt.UUCP>
Date: 5 Apr 93 13:46:28 GMT
References: <9303252134.AA09923@walrus.mvhs.edu>
Sender: news@cs.pitt.edu
Reply-To: geb@cs.pitt.edu (Gordon Banks)
