Subject: Re: tuberculosis
Message-ID: <19434@pitt.UUCP>
Date: 6 Apr 93 16:01:35 GMT
References: <1993Mar25.085526.914@news.wesleyan.edu> <1993Mar26.002229.16888@news.columbia.edu> <1993Mar29.181406.11915@iscsvax.uni.edu>
