Subject: Re: Can't wear contacts after RK/PRK?
Keywords: radial,keratotomy,contact,lenses
Message-ID: <1993Apr16.172052.27843@kestrel.edu>
Date: 16 Apr 93 17:20:52 GMT
Article-I.D.: kestrel.1993Apr16.172052.27843
References: <1993Apr12.130931.27686@cs.ucf.edu> <1993Apr12.140352.963@news.wesleyan.edu> <1993Apr16.063425.163999@zeus.calpoly.edu>
