Subject: Re: Barbecued foods and health risk
Message-ID: <79738@cup.portal.com>
Date: Sat, 17 Apr 93 15:19:11 PDT
Organization: The Portal System (TM)
References:  <C5Mv3v.2o5@world.std.com>
