Subject: Re: Eugenics
Message-ID: <1993Apr18.233114.2556@samba.oit.unc.edu>
Keywords: gene pool; wisdom; virtue
Sender: usenet@samba.oit.unc.edu
Nntp-Posting-Host: naples.med.unc.edu
