From: sasghm@theseus.unx.sas.com (Gary Merrill)
Subject: Re: Science and methodology (was: Homeopathy ... tradition?)
Originator: sasghm@theseus.unx.sas.com
Sender: news@unx.sas.com (Noter of Newsworthy Events)
Message-ID: <C5qG5B.Aro@unx.sas.com>
Date: Mon, 19 Apr 1993 13:29:35 GMT
References: <C5Kv7p.JM3@unx.sas.com> <1993Apr16.155919.28040@cs.rochester.edu> <C5L9ws.Jn2@unx.sas.com> <1993Apr16.210916.6958@cs.rochester.edu>
Nntp-Posting-Host: theseus.unx.sas.com
Organization: SAS Institute Inc.
