Organization: USC  Department of Computer Science
References: <memo.137121@cix.compulink.co.uk> <34513@oasys.dt.navy.mil> <C5qzJM.3wK@news.cso.uiuc.edu> <1qvgit$sbi@agate.berkeley.edu>
Date: 20 Apr 93 06:35:42 GMT
