Subject: Re: OCD
Summary: Here's the highlights from the DSM-IIIR
Message-ID: <1r1djeINNmj8@usenet.pa.dec.com>
Date: 20 Apr 93 20:46:38 GMT
References: <C5r3n6.FG4@news.Hawaii.Edu>
